settings.description: Mario found a fort, and finds out that bowser is inside, will he defeat bowser and escape alive? Or will he fail and lose a life?
Ya know, while fire snakes are meant to be reddish orange... they look really good with a cool blue, so... why not build a nice chilly sky level featuring them for one?~
Pulley Platforms react to the Mario Bros.'s weight. Always keep an eye on both platforms at the same time and make sure you have the room you need to jump!
Use the metal mushroom to get to the top of the temple, where you'll face off against Big Boo!

Welcome to a world where yellow thing-a-majigs reign supreme, giants and petites live in harmony, and corals roam across the night sky. It makes absolutely no sense. 
04/26/22 -- 7:53 A.M.
